python 3.8
pip install -r /path/to/requirements.txt for installing required libraries
download chromedriver from here https://chromedriver.chromium.org/downloads
set your key for 2captcha service in file config.py

to start (before activate your virtual env if you installed it)
python method_with_requests.py
python method_with_selenium.py

in project 2 solution scripts
first method_with_selenium.py use chrome profiles to solving captcha, but solving working not working in headless mode(not suitable for server)
second method_with_requests solve recaptcha v3 by service 2captcha

1 method is just for clarity, use the second one